title: FBI says no terrorism link in NSA gate car crash
text:
FBI says no terrorism link in NSA gate car crash Wednesday, February 14, 2018 - 00:50 
An investigation is underway at the NSA headquarters near Washington where a car crashed into the agency's gates on Wednesday, but officials say there's no link to terrorism. Nathan Frandino reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
